<p>Evesham Community Hospital has 97 beds and provides a wide range of  medical and surgical Inpatient, day case and Outpatient services.</p>
<p>TheÂ Hospital works closely with the Trust community staff, General  Practitioners and other agencies to ensure we all work together for your  benefit as a patient and the benefit of the local community.</p></div>
